*[[美洲菱鮃|美洲菱鮃]] (''Scophthalmus aquosus'')
*[[黑海菱鮃|黑海菱鮃]] (''Scophthalmus maeoticus'')
*[[菱鮃|菱鮃]] (''Scophthalmus rhombus'')
